caption.p: ( a) Radius of gyration for cathepsin L in complex with C1, C2 and C3, ( b) RMSD for cathepsin L in complex with C1, C2 and C3, ( c) RMSF for cathepsin L in complex with C1, C2 and C3, ( d) RMSD of C1, C2 and C3, ( e) Distance of the center of mass of C1, C2 and C3 from the catalytic residue C25 in cathepsin L, and ( f) Distance of the center of mass of C1, C2 and C3 from the catalytic residue H163 in cathepsin L.
